title: Randy Moss Joins The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: Randy Moss Joins The Dan Patrick Show
description:
Dan Patrick is joined by NBC Sports Horse Racing analyst Randy Moss, providing coverage for all eleven-and-a-half hours of this weekend's Breeder's Cup in Del Mar! Get Randy's perspective on Del Mar, the competitors, and more!

Visit BreedersCup.com/2021 for more information and catch all the action on November 5 & 6, only on NBC Sports.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
